<div class="title">The new <strong>plentyShop LTS</strong> online store</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>As of now, online store projects are based on the new online store plugin  <a href="/en/omni-channel/online-store/setting-up-ceres">plentyShop LTS</a>. The <strong>plentyShop LTS</strong> store uses the latest and future-proof <a href="/en/plugins">plugin technology</a>. plentyShop LTS can be customised easily and extended by additional plugins from the <a href="https://marketplace.plentymarkets.com/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">plentyMarketplace</a>&nbsp;<span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-external-link  "></i></span>.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Online stores that have been created on the basis of the old CMS will be maintained during the transition period. However, no new features will be developed for the old CMS. We recommend to use the new <strong>plentyShop LTS</strong> online store for all future online store projects.</p>
</div>
</td>
